steps.apply:
L = {epsilon, 01, 0011, 000111, ...}
- Prefixes of epsilon: {epsilon}
- Prefixes of 01: {epsilon, 0, 01}
- Prefixes of 0011: {epsilon, 0, 00, 001, 0011}
- Prefixes of 000111: {epsilon, 0, 00, 000, 0001, 00011, 000111}
Pattern: prefixes of 0^m 1^m are 0^i for 0<=i<=m, and 0^m 1^j for 1<=j<=m.
So all strings in init(L) have form 0^i 1^j where i >= j >= 0.
